# ============================================================
# HARDENING APPENDIX (added 2026-06-02) — secrets, media, build
# GLOBAL rules: a new companies/<x>/ folder is protected by default.
# Philosophy preserved: scripts, storybooks, manifests, JSON, and
# markdown audit trails stay COMMITTED. Only heavy binaries ignored.
# ============================================================

# --- Secret hygiene (defensive, anywhere in tree) ------------
# Existing `client_secret*.json` misses e.g. healthbrew_client_secret.json.
**/*client_secret*.json
**/*client-secret*.json
**/*-client-secret*.json
**/*service-account*.json
**/*service_account*.json
**/application_default_credentials.json
# OAuth token caches (NARROW — bare *token*.json would eat data files)
**/*.oauth-token.json
**/*-token.json
**/*_token.json
**/token.json
**/.token.json
# Cloud + vendor key files
**/*.gcp.json
**/gcp-key*.json
**/aws-credentials*.json
**/.aws/credentials
# Key material (supplements existing *.pem / *.key)
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks
# Vendor key dumps (Stripe / fal / ElevenLabs / Supabase)
**/stripe-keys*.json
**/*secret_key*.json
**/*-secrets.json
**/*.secrets.json
# Local env variants
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.envrc
# Re-assert example/doc whitelist so the patterns above never eat them
!**/.env.local.example
!**/.env.example
!shared/portfolio-hub/environment-and-secrets.md

# --- Generated/binary media — GLOBAL per-company -------------
companies/*/content/**/*.mp4
companies/*/content/**/*.mov
companies/*/content/**/*.webm
companies/*/content/**/*.mp3
companies/*/content/**/*.wav
companies/*/content/**/*.m4a
companies/*/content/**/*.aac
companies/*/content/**/*.flac
# Heavy still-image SOURCE sheets (Soul/Banana build sources)
companies/*/content/**/_shared/cast/**/*.png
companies/*/content/**/_shared/cast/**/*.psd
companies/*/content/**/_shared/cast/**/*.tiff
# Keep the small functional render refs COMMITTED (negation wins)
!companies/*/content/**/_shared/cast/**/_o1-refs/**/*.jpg
!companies/*/content/**/_shared/cast/**/_o1-refs/**/*.jpeg
# Generic build/scratch dirs anywhere
**/_build/
**/_splice-work*/
**/clips-*/
**/_stills/
**/_stills_*/
**/_renders/
**/_tmp-render*/
# Stray large archives
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.7z
# Stray root marketing PDF (explicit, NOT a global *.pdf ignore —
# the founder commits PDF deliverables/audit artifacts elsewhere)
/MRBEAST-HOW-TO-GO-VIRAL.pdf
